# PR-7a (2026-05): generated declaration files must NOT live under src/.
# tsconfig.build.json correctly emits to dist/, but historic build runs
# left 619 .d.ts artifacts committed under src/. Removed in PR-7a; this
# pattern prevents them from re-entering the tree if a stray local build
# misconfigures emission.
